---
// Galeria.astro — XV Años · Paleta Verde Esmeralda
---

<!-- ONDA CON TEXTO "MI HISTORIA" -->
<section class="relative w-full overflow-hidden" id="galeria-onda">
    <svg
        viewBox="0 0 1080 361"
        preserveAspectRatio="none"
        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
        style="width:100%; display:block; height: clamp(140px, 35vw, 280px);"
    >
        <path
            d="
      M 0,33 10,31 20,30 30,27 40,24 50,22 60,19 70,15 80,13 90,10 100,9 110,8 120,8 130,9 140,10 150,12 160,14 170,17 180,20 190,23 200,26 210,28 220,30 230,32 240,33 250,34 260,34 270,34 280,32 290,31 300,28 310,26 320,23 330,19 340,16 350,13 360,11 370,9 380,8 390,8 400,7 410,8 420,8 430,10 440,11 450,13 460,16 470,19 480,23 490,26 500,28 510,30 520,32 530,33 540,34 550,34 560,34 570,33 580,31 590,30 600,27 610,24 620,21 630,18 640,15 650,13 660,11 670,10 680,10 690,9 700,10 710,10 720,11 730,13 740,15 750,17 760,21 770,23 780,26 790,28 800,30 810,30 820,31 830,31 840,31 850,30 860,28 870,27 880,24 890,22 900,19 910,17 920,14 930,11 940,10 950,8 960,8 970,7 980,7 990,8 1000,8 1010,10 1020,11 1030,13 1040,15 1050,18 1060,21 1070,24 1079,28
      L 1079,349 1070,346 1060,342 1050,339 1040,337 1030,334 1020,332 1010,331 1000,330 990,329 980,329 970,329 960,329 950,330 940,331 930,333 920,335 910,338 900,341 890,344 880,346 870,349 860,350 850,352 840,352 830,353 820,352 810,352 800,351 790,349 780,346 770,344 760,341 750,337 740,335 730,332 720,331 710,330 700,329 690,329 680,329 670,330 660,331 650,332 640,335 630,337 620,341 610,343 600,346 590,348 580,350 570,352 560,352 550,353 540,353 530,352 520,351 510,350 500,348 490,345 480,342 470,339 460,337 450,334 440,332 430,331 420,330 410,330 400,330 390,331 380,331 370,333 360,335 350,337 340,341 330,343 320,346 310,348 300,350 290,352 280,352 270,353 260,353 250,352 240,351 230,350 220,348 210,346 200,343 190,341 180,337 170,335 160,333 150,331 140,330 130,329 120,329 110,328 100,329 90,330 80,330 70,331 60,333 50,335 40,337 30,340 20,343 10,346 0,349
      Z"
            fill="#b2dfc8"></path>
        <foreignObject x="80" y="50" width="920" height="260">
            <div
                style="display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; height:100%; text-align:center;"
            >
                <p
                    class="font-callingstone text-[#1a5c3a] uppercase font-bold text-[30px] sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl tracking-[0.19em]"
                >
                    Mi Historia
                </p>
            </div>
        </foreignObject>
    </svg>
</section>

<!-- CONTENIDO -->
<section class="py-6 px-4 relative overflow-hidden" id="seccion-galeria">
    <div class="max-w-sm mx-auto relative z-10">
        <!-- Línea decorativa -->
        <div
            class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 mb-6"
            id="linea-deco"
        >
            <div
                style="height:1px; width:60px; background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, #50C878);"
            >
            </div>
            <span class="font-allura text-[#50C878]" style="font-size:1.4rem;"
                >✦</span
            >
            <div
                style="height:1px; width:60px; background: linear-gradient(to left, transparent, #50C878);"
            >
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- TEXTO SIN CARD -->
        <div class="mb-10 px-2" id="texto-historia">
            <p
                class="font-callingstone text-base text-[#1a5c3a] tracking-widest leading-relaxed text-center mb-4"
            >
                Caminé por los pasillos de la vida sin saber que el destino me
                tenía guardado el momento más especial. Una sonrisa en el lugar
                menos esperado fue el inicio de esta historia.
            </p>
            <div class="flex justify-center my-3">
                <div class="w-8 h-px bg-[#50C878]/60"></div>
            </div>
            <p
                class="font-callingstone text-base text-[#1a5c3a] tracking-widest leading-relaxed text-center mb-4"
            >
                Juntos con quienes más amo descubrí que la felicidad vive en
                los detalles, en las risas que no terminan y en esos abrazos
                que curan todo.
            </p>
            <div class="flex justify-center my-3">
                <div class="w-8 h-px bg-[#50C878]/60"></div>
            </div>
            <p
                class="font-callingstone text-base text-[#1a5c3a] tracking-widest leading-relaxed text-center mb-4"
            >
                Entendí que la vida es el viaje más valioso y hoy decido
                celebrar quince años recorriendo cada paso con gratitud y amor.
            </p>
            <div class="flex justify-center my-3">
                <div class="w-8 h-px bg-[#50C878]/60"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="relative w-full h-32 pointer-events-none mb-2">
                <img
                    src="/imagenes/florabajo.png"
                    alt=""
                    class="absolute bottom-10 -right-3 w-56 sm:w-44 object-contain z-20 scale-x-[-1]"
                    id="flor-galeria"
                    style="filter: hue-rotate(100deg) saturate(1.2);"
                />
            </div>
            <p
                class="font-callingstone text-base text-[#50C878] leading-relaxed text-center font-bold tracking-widest"
            >
                Mis XV son una celebración del amor, pero también de la amistad
                y la familia.
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- CARRUSEL -->
        <div id="galeria-wrapper" class="relative w-full">
            <div
                class="absolute -inset-3 rounded-[2rem] pointer-events-none z-0"
            >
                <div
                    class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-8 h-8 border-t-2 border-l-2 border-[#50C878]/40 rounded-tl-2xl"
                >
                </div>
                <div
                    class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-8 h-8 border-t-2 border-r-2 border-[#50C878]/40 rounded-tr-2xl"
                >
                </div>
                <div
                    class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-8 h-8 border-b-2 border-l-2 border-[#50C878]/40 rounded-bl-2xl"
                >
                </div>
                <div
                    class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-8 h-8 border-b-2 border-r-2 border-[#50C878]/40 rounded-br-2xl"
                >
                </div>
            </div>

            <div
                class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-[1.5rem] z-10"
                id="slides-viewport"
                style="aspect-ratio: 3/4;"
            >
            </div>

            <!-- Gradiente inferior -->
            <div
                class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 h-32 z-20 pointer-events-none rounded-b-[1.5rem]"
                style="background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(0,0,0,0.45), transparent);"
            >
            </div>

            <!-- Número de slide -->
            <div
                class="absolute bottom-5 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 z-30 flex items-center gap-3"
            >
                <div class="w-6 h-px bg-white/40"></div>
                <span
                    id="num-slide"
                    class="font-cathylise text-white/80 text-lg tracking-widest"
                    >01</span
                >
                <div class="w-6 h-px bg-white/40"></div>
            </div>

            <!-- Progreso circular -->
            <div class="absolute top-4 right-4 z-30">
                <svg
                    width="36"
                    height="36"
                    viewBox="0 0 36 36"
                    class="rotate-[-90deg]"
                >
                    <circle
                        cx="18"
                        cy="18"
                        r="15"
                        fill="none"
                        stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.15)"
                        stroke-width="2"></circle>
                    <circle
                        id="progreso-circulo"
                        cx="18"
                        cy="18"
                        r="15"
                        fill="none"
                        stroke="rgba(80,200,120,0.9)"
                        stroke-width="2"
                        stroke-dasharray="94.2"
                        stroke-dashoffset="94.2"
                        stroke-linecap="round"></circle>
                </svg>
            </div>

            <!-- Dots laterales -->
            <div
                class="absolute left-3 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 z-30 flex flex-col gap-2"
                id="dots-lateral"
            >
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- MINIATURAS -->
        <div class="mt-4 mb-2" id="miniaturas-container">
            <div
                class="flex gap-2 overflow-x-auto pb-2 snap-x snap-mandatory"
                id="miniaturas-track"
                style="scrollbar-width: none; -ms-overflow-style: none;"
            >
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- BOTÓN VER GALERÍA -->
        <div class="flex justify-center mt-6 mb-2" id="btn-galeria-container">
            <button
                id="btn-ver-galeria"
                class="boton-galeria group font-callingstone"
            >
                <svg
                    class="w-4 h-4 transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:-translate-y-0.5"
                    fill="none"
                    stroke="currentColor"
                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                >
                    <rect
                        x="3"
                        y="3"
                        width="7"
                        height="7"
                        rx="1"
                        stroke-width="1.5"></rect>
                    <rect
                        x="14"
                        y="3"
                        width="7"
                        height="7"
                        rx="1"
                        stroke-width="1.5"></rect>
                    <rect
                        x="3"
                        y="14"
                        width="7"
                        height="7"
                        rx="1"
                        stroke-width="1.5"></rect>
                    <rect
                        x="14"
                        y="14"
                        width="7"
                        height="7"
                        rx="1"
                        stroke-width="1.5"></rect>
                </svg>
                Ver Galería
            </button>
        </div>

        <!-- Crédito -->
        <div
            class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4 mt-4"
            id="credito-galeria"
        >
            <div
                style="height:1px; flex:1; background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, #50C878);"
            >
            </div>
            <span
                class="font-callingstone text-[#50C878]/60 text-xs tracking-[0.3em] uppercase"
                >Mi historia</span
            >
            <div
                style="height:1px; flex:1; background: linear-gradient(to left, transparent, #50C878);"
            >
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- MODAL FULLSCREEN -->
    <div
        id="modal-galeria"
        class="fixed inset-0 z-50 hidden items-center justify-center"
        style="background: rgba(0,0,0,0.96);"
    >
        <div
            class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none overflow-hidden"
            id="modal-particulas"
        >
        </div>

        <button
            id="cerrar-modal"
            class="absolute top-6 right-6 w-12 h-12 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center transition-all duration-500 z-50 hover:rotate-90"
            style="background: rgba(80,200,120,0.15); border: 1px solid rgba(80,200,120,0.3);"
        >
            <svg
                class="w-5 h-5"
                fill="none"
                stroke="#50C878"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            >
                <path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    stroke-width="2"
                    d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"></path>
            </svg>
        </button>

        <div
            class="relative w-full h-full flex items-center justify-center px-4 md:px-20"
        >
            <button
                id="btn-anterior"
                class="absolute left-3 md:left-8 z-40 w-12 h-12 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-110"
                style="background: rgba(80,200,120,0.12); border: 1px solid rgba(80,200,120,0.25);"
            >
                <svg
                    class="w-6 h-6"
                    fill="none"
                    stroke="#50C878"
                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                >
                    <path
                        stroke-linecap="round"
                        stroke-linejoin="round"
                        stroke-width="2"
                        d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"></path>
                </svg>
            </button>

            <div
                class="relative w-full max-w-xs md:max-w-md z-30"
                id="modal-contenido"
            >
                <div class="absolute -inset-4 pointer-events-none">
                    <div
                        class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-6 h-6 border-t border-l border-[#50C878]/30"
                    >
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-6 h-6 border-t border-r border-[#50C878]/30"
                    >
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-6 h-6 border-b border-l border-[#50C878]/30"
                    >
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-6 h-6 border-b border-r border-[#50C878]/30"
                    >
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div id="modal-track" class="flex will-change-transform"></div>
                <div
                    class="absolute -bottom-10 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 flex items-center gap-3 whitespace-nowrap"
                >
                    <span
                        id="modal-num"
                        class="font-cathylise text-[#50C878]/70 text-base"
                        >01</span
                    >
                    <div class="flex gap-1" id="modal-dots-mini"></div>
                    <span
                        class="font-cathylise text-white/30 text-base"
                        id="modal-total">05</span
                    >
                </div>
            </div>

            <button
                id="btn-siguiente"
                class="absolute right-3 md:right-8 z-40 w-12 h-12 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-110"
                style="background: rgba(80,200,120,0.12); border: 1px solid rgba(80,200,120,0.25);"
            >
                <svg
                    class="w-6 h-6"
                    fill="none"
                    stroke="#50C878"
                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                >
                    <path
                        stroke-linecap="round"
                        stroke-linejoin="round"
                        stroke-width="2"
                        d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"></path>
                </svg>
            </button>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<script>
    import { gsap } from "gsap";
    import { ScrollTrigger } from "gsap/ScrollTrigger";
    gsap.registerPlugin(ScrollTrigger);

    if (typeof window !== "undefined") {
        document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", () => {
            // ── ANIMACIONES DE ENTRADA ──
            gsap.set("#galeria-onda", { opacity: 0, y: -20 });
            gsap.set("#linea-deco", { opacity: 0 });
            gsap.set("#texto-historia", { opacity: 0, y: 20 });
            gsap.set("#flor-galeria", { opacity: 0, x: 30 });
            gsap.set("#galeria-wrapper", { opacity: 0, scale: 0.96 });
            gsap.set("#miniaturas-container", { opacity: 0, y: 10 });
            gsap.set("#btn-galeria-container", { opacity: 0, y: 10 });
            gsap.set("#credito-galeria", { opacity: 0 });

            ScrollTrigger.create({
                trigger: "#seccion-galeria",
                start: "top 85%",
                onEnter: () => {
                    const tl = gsap.timeline();
                    tl.to("#galeria-onda", {
                        opacity: 1,
                        y: 0,
                        duration: 0.8,
                        ease: "power2.out",
                    })
                        .to(
                            "#linea-deco",
                            { opacity: 1, duration: 0.6 },
                            "-=0.3",
                        )
                        .to(
                            "#texto-historia",
                            {
                                opacity: 1,
                                y: 0,
                                duration: 0.8,
                                ease: "power2.out",
                            },
                            "-=0.3",
                        )
                        .to(
                            "#flor-galeria",
                            {
                                opacity: 1,
                                x: 0,
                                duration: 0.7,
                                ease: "power2.out",
                            },
                            "-=0.4",
                        )
                        .to(
                            "#galeria-wrapper",
                            {
                                opacity: 1,
                                scale: 1,
                                duration: 1,
                                ease: "power3.out",
                            },
                            "-=0.3",
                        )
                        .to(
                            "#miniaturas-container",
                            {
                                opacity: 1,
                                y: 0,
                                duration: 0.6,
                                ease: "power2.out",
                            },
                            "-=0.2",
                        )
                        .to(
                            "#btn-galeria-container",
                            {
                                opacity: 1,
                                y: 0,
                                duration: 0.6,
                                ease: "back.out(1.5)",
                            },
                            "-=0.3",
                        )
                        .to(
                            "#credito-galeria",
                            { opacity: 1, duration: 0.6 },
                            "-=0.3",
                        );
                },
                onLeaveBack: () => {
                    gsap.set("#galeria-onda", { opacity: 0, y: -20 });
                    gsap.set("#linea-deco", { opacity: 0 });
                    gsap.set("#texto-historia", { opacity: 0, y: 20 });
                    gsap.set("#flor-galeria", { opacity: 0, x: 30 });
                    gsap.set("#galeria-wrapper", { opacity: 0, scale: 0.96 });
                    gsap.set("#miniaturas-container", { opacity: 0, y: 10 });
                    gsap.set("#btn-galeria-container", { opacity: 0, y: 10 });
                    gsap.set("#credito-galeria", { opacity: 0 });
                },
            });

            // ── FOTOS: foto1.png → foto5.png ──
            const fotos = [
                { src: "/imagenes/foto1.png", alt: "Mi historia 1" },
                { src: "/imagenes/foto2.png", alt: "Mi historia 2" },
                { src: "/imagenes/foto3.png", alt: "Mi historia 3" },
                { src: "/imagenes/foto4.png", alt: "Mi historia 4" },
                { src: "/imagenes/foto5.png", alt: "Mi historia 5" },
            ];

            const DURACION = 4500;
            const CIRCUNFERENCIA = 94.2;
            const viewport = document.getElementById("slides-viewport");
            const dotsLateral = document.getElementById("dots-lateral");
            const numSlide = document.getElementById("num-slide");
            const progresoCirculo = document.getElementById("progreso-circulo");
            const miniaturasTrack = document.getElementById("miniaturas-track");

            fotos.forEach((foto, i) => {
                if (!viewport) return;
                const slide = document.createElement("div");
                slide.className = "slide-item absolute inset-0 cursor-pointer";
                slide.setAttribute("data-index", i.toString());
                slide.style.cssText = `opacity:${i === 0 ? "1" : "0"}; z-index:${i === 0 ? "2" : "1"};`;
                slide.innerHTML = `
                    <div class="w-full h-full overflow-hidden">
                        <img src="${foto.src}" alt="${foto.alt}"
                            class="slide-img w-full h-full object-cover"
                            style="transform-origin: center center;" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="absolute inset-0"
                        style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(80,200,120,0.08) 0%, transparent 50%, rgba(26,92,58,0.06) 100%);">
                    </div>
                    <div class="slide-hover-icon absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center opacity-0 transition-opacity duration-500">
                        <div class="relative">
                            <div class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center"
                                style="background: rgba(80,200,120,0.2); backdrop-filter: blur(8px); border: 1px solid rgba(80,200,120,0.4);">
                                <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="#50C878" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                    <circle cx="10.5" cy="10.5" r="6.5" stroke-width="1.5"></circle>
                                    <path d="M15.5 15.5L21 21" stroke-width="1.5"></path>
                                </svg>
                            </div>
                            <div class="absolute inset-0 rounded-full animate-ping"
                                style="border: 1px solid rgba(80,200,120,0.3);"></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                `;
                slide.addEventListener("mouseenter", () => {
                    const icon = slide.querySelector(
                        ".slide-hover-icon",
                    ) as HTMLElement;
                    if (icon) icon.style.opacity = "1";
                });
                slide.addEventListener("mouseleave", () => {
                    const icon = slide.querySelector(
                        ".slide-hover-icon",
                    ) as HTMLElement;
                    if (icon) icon.style.opacity = "0";
                });
                slide.addEventListener("click", () => abrirModal(i));
                viewport.appendChild(slide);

                if (dotsLateral) {
                    const dot = document.createElement("div");
                    dot.className =
                        "dot-lat transition-all duration-500 rounded-full";
                    dot.style.cssText = `width:${i === 0 ? "8px" : "4px"}; height:${i === 0 ? "8px" : "4px"}; background:${i === 0 ? "rgba(80,200,120,0.9)" : "rgba(80,200,120,0.3)"}`;
                    dotsLateral.appendChild(dot);
                }

                if (miniaturasTrack) {
                    const mini = document.createElement("button");
                    mini.className =
                        "miniatura-btn flex-shrink-0 snap-start rounded-xl overflow-hidden";
                    mini.setAttribute("data-mini", i.toString());
                    mini.style.cssText = `width:52px; height:52px; border:2px solid ${i === 0 ? "rgba(80,200,120,0.9)" : "rgba(80,200,120,0.2)"}; opacity:${i === 0 ? "1" : "0.6"};`;
                    mini.innerHTML = `<img src="${foto.src}" alt="${foto.alt}" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />`;
                    mini.addEventListener("click", () => {
                        irASlide(i);
                        clearTimeout(autoTimer);
                        programarSiguiente();
                    });
                    miniaturasTrack.appendChild(mini);
                }
            });

            let kbTween: gsap.core.Tween | null = null;
            function iniciarKenBurns(index: number) {
                if (kbTween) kbTween.kill();
                const slides = document.querySelectorAll(".slide-item");
                const img = slides[index]?.querySelector(
                    ".slide-img",
                ) as HTMLElement;
                if (!img) return;
                gsap.set(img, { scale: 1, x: "0%", y: "0%" });
                const dirs = [
                    { scale: 1.08, x: "-2%", y: "-2%" },
                    { scale: 1.08, x: "2%", y: "-1%" },
                    { scale: 1.06, x: "-1%", y: "2%" },
                    { scale: 1.07, x: "1%", y: "-2%" },
                    { scale: 1.06, x: "-2%", y: "1%" },
                ];
                const d = dirs[index % dirs.length];
                kbTween = gsap.to(img, {
                    scale: d.scale,
                    x: d.x,
                    y: d.y,
                    duration: DURACION / 1000 + 1,
                    ease: "none",
                });
            }

            let progresoTween: gsap.core.Tween | null = null;
            function iniciarProgreso() {
                if (progresoTween) progresoTween.kill();
                if (!progresoCirculo) return;
                gsap.set(progresoCirculo, { strokeDashoffset: CIRCUNFERENCIA });
                progresoTween = gsap.to(progresoCirculo, {
                    strokeDashoffset: 0,
                    duration: DURACION / 1000,
                    ease: "none",
                });
            }

            let slideActual = 0;
            let autoTimer: any;
            let pausado = false;
            let rafId: number | null = null;

            function actualizarDots(index: number) {
                document.querySelectorAll(".dot-lat").forEach((d, i) => {
                    const el = d as HTMLElement;
                    el.style.width = i === index ? "8px" : "4px";
                    el.style.height = i === index ? "8px" : "4px";
                    el.style.background =
                        i === index
                            ? "rgba(80,200,120,0.9)"
                            : "rgba(80,200,120,0.3)";
                });
                if (numSlide)
                    numSlide.textContent = String(index + 1).padStart(2, "0");

                document.querySelectorAll(".miniatura-btn").forEach((m, i) => {
                    const el = m as HTMLElement;
                    el.style.border =
                        i === index
                            ? "2px solid rgba(80,200,120,0.9)"
                            : "2px solid rgba(80,200,120,0.2)";
                    el.style.opacity = i === index ? "1" : "0.6";
                });

                const miniActiva = document.querySelector(
                    `[data-mini="${index}"]`,
                ) as HTMLElement;
                const track = document.getElementById("miniaturas-track");
                if (miniActiva && track) {
                    const offsetLeft =
                        miniActiva.offsetLeft -
                        track.clientWidth / 2 +
                        miniActiva.clientWidth / 2;
                    track.scrollTo({ left: offsetLeft, behavior: "smooth" });
                }
            }

            function irASlide(nuevoIndex: number) {
                if (rafId !== null) cancelAnimationFrame(rafId);

                const slides = document.querySelectorAll(".slide-item");
                const anterior = slideActual;
                slideActual = (nuevoIndex + fotos.length) % fotos.length;

                const slideAnterior = slides[anterior] as HTMLElement;
                const slideSiguiente = slides[slideActual] as HTMLElement;

                slideAnterior.style.zIndex = "2";
                slideSiguiente.style.zIndex = "3";
                slideSiguiente.style.opacity = "0";

                const duracionMs = 1400;
                let start: number | null = null;

                function frame(ts: number) {
                    if (!start) start = ts;
                    const t = Math.min((ts - start) / duracionMs, 1);
                    const ease =
                        t < 0.5 ? 2 * t * t : 1 - Math.pow(-2 * t + 2, 2) / 2;
                    slideSiguiente.style.opacity = String(ease);
                    slideAnterior.style.opacity = String(1 - ease);

                    if (t < 1) {
                        rafId = requestAnimationFrame(frame);
                    } else {
                        slideSiguiente.style.opacity = "1";
                        slideSiguiente.style.zIndex = "2";
                        slideAnterior.style.opacity = "0";
                        slideAnterior.style.zIndex = "1";
                        rafId = null;
                    }
                }

                rafId = requestAnimationFrame(frame);
                actualizarDots(slideActual);
                iniciarKenBurns(slideActual);
                iniciarProgreso();
            }

            function programarSiguiente() {
                clearTimeout(autoTimer);
                autoTimer = setTimeout(() => {
                    if (!pausado) {
                        irASlide(slideActual + 1);
                        programarSiguiente();
                    }
                }, DURACION);
            }

            const wrapper = document.getElementById("galeria-wrapper");
            wrapper?.addEventListener("mouseenter", () => {
                pausado = true;
                progresoTween?.pause();
                kbTween?.pause();
            });
            wrapper?.addEventListener("mouseleave", () => {
                pausado = false;
                progresoTween?.resume();
                kbTween?.resume();
                programarSiguiente();
            });

            let touchX = 0;
            viewport?.addEventListener(
                "touchstart",
                (e) => {
                    touchX = e.touches[0].clientX;
                },
                { passive: true },
            );
            viewport?.addEventListener("touchend", (e) => {
                const diff = touchX - e.changedTouches[0].clientX;
                if (Math.abs(diff) > 50) {
                    irASlide(diff > 0 ? slideActual + 1 : slideActual - 1);
                    programarSiguiente();
                }
            });

            iniciarKenBurns(0);
            actualizarDots(0);

            // ── INTERSECTION OBSERVER ──
            const observerGaleria = new IntersectionObserver(
                (entries) => {
                    entries.forEach((entry) => {
                        if (entry.isIntersecting) {
                            pausado = false;
                            iniciarProgreso();
                            programarSiguiente();
                        } else {
                            pausado = true;
                            clearTimeout(autoTimer);
                            autoTimer = null;
                            progresoTween?.pause();
                            kbTween?.pause();
                            if (rafId !== null) {
                                cancelAnimationFrame(rafId);
                                rafId = null;
                            }
                        }
                    });
                },
                { threshold: 0, rootMargin: "0px" },
            );

            const galeriaSection = document.getElementById("seccion-galeria");
            if (galeriaSection) observerGaleria.observe(galeriaSection);

            // ── MODAL ──
            const modal = document.getElementById("modal-galeria");
            const modalTrack = document.getElementById("modal-track");
            const modalNum = document.getElementById("modal-num");
            const modalTotal = document.getElementById("modal-total");
            const modalDotsMini = document.getElementById("modal-dots-mini");
            const btnAnterior = document.getElementById("btn-anterior");
            const btnSiguiente = document.getElementById("btn-siguiente");
            const cerrarModalBtn = document.getElementById("cerrar-modal");
            const btnVerGaleria = document.getElementById("btn-ver-galeria");

            if (modalTotal)
                modalTotal.textContent = String(fotos.length).padStart(2, "0");

            fotos.forEach((foto) => {
                if (!modalTrack) return;
                const slide = document.createElement("div");
                slide.className =
                    "min-w-full flex items-center justify-center px-2";
                slide.innerHTML = `
                    <div class="relative w-full rounded-2xl overflow-hidden" style="border:1px solid rgba(80,200,120,0.15);">
                        <img src="${foto.src}" alt="${foto.alt}" class="w-full h-auto max-h-[80vh] object-contain" style="background:rgba(0,0,0,0.3);" />
                    </div>
                `;
                modalTrack.appendChild(slide);
            });

            fotos.forEach((_, i) => {
                if (!modalDotsMini) return;
                const d = document.createElement("div");
                d.className = "modal-dot-mini rounded-full";
                d.style.cssText = `width:${i === 0 ? "16px" : "4px"}; height:4px; background:${i === 0 ? "rgba(80,200,120,0.8)" : "rgba(80,200,120,0.2)"}; transition:all 0.4s;`;
                modalDotsMini.appendChild(d);
            });

            let indiceModal = 0;

            function actualizarModalDots(index: number) {
                document.querySelectorAll(".modal-dot-mini").forEach((d, i) => {
                    const el = d as HTMLElement;
                    el.style.width = i === index ? "16px" : "4px";
                    el.style.background =
                        i === index
                            ? "rgba(80,200,120,0.8)"
                            : "rgba(80,200,120,0.2)";
                });
                if (modalNum)
                    modalNum.textContent = String(index + 1).padStart(2, "0");
            }

            const moverModal = (nuevo: number, animar = true) => {
                if (!modalTrack) return;
                indiceModal = (nuevo + fotos.length) % fotos.length;
                if (animar) {
                    gsap.to(modalTrack, {
                        x: `-${indiceModal * 100}%`,
                        duration: 0.6,
                        ease: "power3.out",
                    });
                } else {
                    gsap.set(modalTrack, { x: `-${indiceModal * 100}%` });
                }
                actualizarModalDots(indiceModal);
            };

            function crearParticulas() {
                const container = document.getElementById("modal-particulas");
                if (!container) return;
                container.innerHTML = "";
                for (let i = 0; i < 12; i++) {
                    const p = document.createElement("div");
                    p.style.cssText = `position:absolute; width:${Math.random() * 3 + 1}px; height:${Math.random() * 3 + 1}px; background:rgba(80,200,120,${Math.random() * 0.3 + 0.1}); border-radius:50%; left:${Math.random() * 100}%; top:${Math.random() * 100}%;`;
                    container.appendChild(p);
                    gsap.to(p, {
                        y: -30 - Math.random() * 40,
                        x: (Math.random() - 0.5) * 20,
                        opacity: 0,
                        duration: 3 + Math.random() * 4,
                        repeat: -1,
                        delay: Math.random() * 3,
                        ease: "none",
                    });
                }
            }

            const abrirModal = (indice: number) => {
                if (!modal) return;
                pausado = true;
                clearTimeout(autoTimer);
                progresoTween?.pause();
                kbTween?.pause();
                modal.classList.remove("hidden");
                modal.classList.add("flex");
                document.body.style.overflow = "hidden";
                moverModal(indice, false);
                crearParticulas();
                gsap.fromTo(
                    modal,
                    { opacity: 0 },
                    { opacity: 1, duration: 0.5, ease: "power2.out" },
                );
                gsap.fromTo(
                    "#modal-contenido",
                    { scale: 0.88, opacity: 0, y: 20 },
                    {
                        scale: 1,
                        opacity: 1,
                        y: 0,
                        duration: 0.7,
                        ease: "power3.out",
                        delay: 0.1,
                    },
                );
            };

            const cerrarModalFn = () => {
                if (!modal) return;
                gsap.to("#modal-contenido", {
                    scale: 0.88,
                    opacity: 0,
                    y: 20,
                    duration: 0.4,
                    ease: "power2.in",
                });
                gsap.to(modal, {
                    opacity: 0,
                    duration: 0.4,
                    ease: "power2.in",
                    delay: 0.15,
                    onComplete: () => {
                        modal.classList.add("hidden");
                        modal.classList.remove("flex");
                        document.body.style.overflow = "";
                        pausado = false;
                        iniciarProgreso();
                        programarSiguiente();
                    },
                });
            };

            btnVerGaleria?.addEventListener("click", () => abrirModal(0));
            btnAnterior?.addEventListener("click", (e) => {
                e.stopPropagation();
                moverModal(indiceModal - 1);
            });
            btnSiguiente?.addEventListener("click", (e) => {
                e.stopPropagation();
                moverModal(indiceModal + 1);
            });
            cerrarModalBtn?.addEventListener("click", (e) => {
                e.stopPropagation();
                cerrarModalFn();
            });
            modal?.addEventListener("click", (e) => {
                if (e.target === modal) cerrarModalFn();
            });

            document.addEventListener("keydown", (e) => {
                if (modal && !modal.classList.contains("hidden")) {
                    if (e.key === "Escape") cerrarModalFn();
                    if (e.key === "ArrowLeft") moverModal(indiceModal - 1);
                    if (e.key === "ArrowRight") moverModal(indiceModal + 1);
                }
            });

            let mTouchX = 0;
            modal?.addEventListener(
                "touchstart",
                (e) => {
                    mTouchX = e.touches[0].clientX;
                },
                { passive: true },
            );
            modal?.addEventListener("touchend", (e) => {
                const diff = mTouchX - e.changedTouches[0].clientX;
                if (Math.abs(diff) > 60)
                    moverModal(diff > 0 ? indiceModal + 1 : indiceModal - 1);
            });
        });
    }
</script>

<style>
    #slides-viewport {
        position: relative;
        contain: strict;
        will-change: transform;
    }
    .slide-item {
        will-change: opacity;
        contain: layout style;
    }
    .slide-img {
        will-change: transform;
    }
    #modal-track {
        will-change: transform;
        display: flex;
    }
    #miniaturas-track::-webkit-scrollbar {
        display: none;
    }
    .miniatura-btn {
        transition:
            border 0.3s,
            opacity 0.3s;
    }
    .miniatura-btn:hover {
        opacity: 1 !important;
        transform: scale(1.08);
    }
    /* Botón principal — verde esmeralda */
    .boton-galeria {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 8px;
        padding: 10px 28px;
        background: #50C878;
        color: white;
        border: none;
        border-radius: 50px;
        font-size: 14px;
        font-weight: 600;
        letter-spacing: 0.2em;
        cursor: pointer;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    .boton-galeria:hover {
        background: #1a5c3a;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(80, 200, 120, 0.4);
        transform: translateY(-2px);
    }
    @keyframes ping {
        75%,
        100% {
            transform: scale(1.6);
            opacity: 0;
        }
    }
    .animate-ping {
        animation: ping 1.5s cubic-bezier(0, 0, 0.2, 1) infinite;
    }
</style>